Architecture: all
Depends: python, python-libvirt, qemu, python-lockfile, python-enum34, python-texttable, python-paramiko, python-cheetah, libvirt-bin, python-argcomplete, python-netifaces, python-pbkdf2, python-ldap, python-serial, mcvirt-common=%VERSION%
